WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Have you ever tried to use the native R pipe and then encounter this error?

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.360
The native R pipe takes the object on the left and places it as the first argument of

00:00:08.360 --> 00:00:09.360
the argument on the right.

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:14.080
It's very similar to the pipe from Magritter, but the native R pipe has a few differences.

00:00:14.080 --> 00:00:17.559
The dot syntax is a feature of Magritter and not of base R.

00:00:17.559 --> 00:00:22.440
So this works because it's the same as this, but this doesn't because it doesn't know

00:00:22.440 --> 00:00:24.000
what to do with that dot.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:27.200
So you have to create what is called an anonymous function.

00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:28.200
Let's break it down.

00:00:29.040 --> 00:00:32.740
This is what's being passed into the pipe, native pipe operator.

00:00:32.740 --> 00:00:36.400
It takes the object on the left and places it as the first argument of the function on

00:00:36.400 --> 00:00:37.400
the right.

00:00:37.400 --> 00:00:41.919
The anonymous function definition, the formal argument or parameter, which is the variable

00:00:41.919 --> 00:00:45.400
name in this case, a dot, the function body.

00:00:45.400 --> 00:00:51.400
This is the actual work being done using the argument we defined and the immediate invocation.

00:00:51.400 --> 00:00:56.480
And these trailing parentheses tell R, execute this function I just defined right now.

00:00:56.480 --> 00:00:57.480
And it works.

00:00:57.759 --> 00:01:01.279
There's also an anonymous function shortcut, so you can run this instead.

00:01:01.279 --> 00:01:05.239
And if you don't want a dot, you could use other name like X, or you can be explicit

00:01:05.239 --> 00:01:06.239
and say data.

00:01:06.239 --> 00:01:11.239
Now there's an even easier way of writing this using the pipe placeholder from R 4.2.

00:01:11.239 --> 00:01:13.400
Are you interested in learning about the placeholder?

00:01:13.400 --> 00:01:14.279
Let us know in the comments.

